Exhibit Hall Only Pass: What's Included

Register for the Exhibit Hall Only Pass and get access to all this:

     * Exhibit Hall - Talk with Fluent's exhibitors, test drive new tools,
       compare products, spend time with speakers and authors, and much
       more
     * Office Hours - Meet with experts and Fluent speakers at their
       Office Hours
     * Sponsored Sessions - Attend all the sessions in the sponsored
       sessions track
     * Web Platform Document Sprint - Join like-minded contributors and
       help to document the Web Platform and improve the WebPlatform.org
       user experience (separate registration rquired)
     * Women's Communities Meetup - In addition to great networking, hear
       lightning talks from representatives of groups, companies, and
       projects that support diversity in the technology community
     * Ignite Fluent - Be enlightened by fast-paced 5 minute presenations
       in this high-energy technology show-and-tell
     * Speed Networking - Jumpstart your networking with other attendees
     * Flocks - Join the conversation at these informal gatherings with
       experts, developers, and evangelists organized around specific
       topics (Web Performance, Angular, and Ember.js)
     * Birds of a Feather (BoF) lunch sessions - Discuss and share ideas
       around a particular topic with other Fluent attendees over lunch
     * FluentConf Survivor Challenge - Test your coding skills and compete
       for prizes, fame, and glory
     * Exhibit Hall Reception - Grab a drink, mingle with fellow
       attendees, and see the latest in web platform technologies and
       products from leading companies
     * Hardware Showcase - Check out some of the most innovative hardware
       projects and see what javascript can do
     * Closing Reception - Join us for a drink and one last chance to
       connect in-person with fellow developers
     * The Community Lounge - Take a breather in the Community Lounge
       (sponsored by Google) to gather with other brilliant minds, hack on
       your latest project, or just get a break from the day's sessions
     * The hallway track - Fluent's hallways have been the birthplace of
       many ideas and collaborations. The hallway track, as we like to
       call it, is one of the best parts of Fluent

